projects.title: Women Black&White Prints
projects.description: “Naked and Not Stripped” is an art collection created from 2017 to 2019 that was exhibited in New York city and Chicago USA as well as in Casablanca Morocco. In order to make this collection available and affordable to my awesome art clients, we’ve made limited hand signed edition prints, on a premium paper and different sizes starting $150. The prints come unframed
